== Custom keybindings ==
Add Alt+Tab shortcut to switch to previous window.
{{emerge|media-sound/mpc}}
{{file|rc.conf|Volume keybindings|<pre>
-- {{{ Key bindings
globalkeys = awful.util.table.join(
...
    -- alt + tab
    awful.key({ "Mod1", }, "Tab",
        function ()
            awful.client.focus.history.previous()
            if client.focus then
                client.focus:raise()
            end
        end),
</pre>}}


